{"tid":1755144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[埋單計左數] 中共今次約有49萬鐵票，平均每個選區為1082票","createTime":"2019-11-25T12:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T05:30:32.000Z","uid":37232,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff176f222ad9c0b4d2a7b16436b6621114640eb","tid":1755144,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"何謂鐵票？是指平時唔出現，民調搵佢唔到，但選舉就會出現的人/票<br />\n<br />\n反對派得票：1,673,834<br />\n建制派得票：1,206,645<br />\nref：<a href=\"https://dce2019.thestandnews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdce2019.thestandnews.com%2F&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=1cb1cdd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdce2019.thestandnews.com%2F&h=c06c5bb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://dce2019.thestandnews.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n11月15日至11月20日最近民調：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/s/6th_round.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fs%2F6th_round.pdf&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=9316ac99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/s/6th_round.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n對特區政府嘅信任程度，不信任：一般：信任：不知道&amp;難說 = 64.8%：15.8%：18.5%：0.9%<br />\n<br />\n對中央政府嘅信任程度，不信任：一般：信任：不知道&amp;難說 = 61.6%：10.6%：25.7%：2.1%<br />\n<br />\n對警⽅嘅信任程度，不信任：一般：信任：不知道&amp;難說 = 63.1%：8.5%：27.3%：1.2%<br />\n<br />\n先將不知道&amp;難說撇除，並將一般信任度的一半當作不信任，再將三個對建制有關的調查取平均值，不信任：信任 = 70%：30%<br />\n<br />\n假設信任者會投建制派，不信任者會投反對派。<br />\n<br />\n以此比例計算，建制非鐵票 = 反對派得票 &divide; 70% &times; 30% = 717,357<br />\n<br />\n中共鐵票 = 建制派得票 - 建制非鐵票 = 489,288 ~ 49萬票<br />\n<br />\n以452區計，平均每個選區為1082票。"},{"pid":"000afa0b0e8aa399bf97100fbcd4c59ca2eb82da","tid":1755144,"uid":25012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"光復大嶼山<br />\n<br />\n佢有份和議明日大嶼願景<br />\n佢有份提名林鄭月娥<br />\n佢支持一地兩檢<br />\n<br />\n唔睇實<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">余漢坤</span></strong></span>呢個人，出年可能過埋一兆人工島<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754646</a>"},{"pid":"f531f32fd8bfdab09d3e3a859d1e2f192bb5ae19","tid":1755144,"uid":244240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85add9d73722a1cbcbff456376848068814edd56","tid":1755144,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"如果當埋俾10分信任政府的死硬派為鐵票會再多約17萬票，總鐵票會是66萬票"},{"pid":"971fa307029b5c44ec5ea137590d53d36ffdfb37","tid":1755144,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4885de0c2b979d8e2c02a8baed027de885e8702","tid":1755144,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8b23cbc270be82d82d4f4ed35ca3afb1b2e34e","tid":1755144,"uid":22844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db31512c297af37b5f41ff34ab0db5afd7633ba9","tid":1755144,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8231dc11f70795b069045ab79f2f8bb02bf4ee72","tid":1755144,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346dd976c8ecfb62e178e6226fac50ce70d162bf","tid":1755144,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}